hadiths[7]{hadithnumber,text}:
192,The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) used to eat cucumbers with ripe dates.”
193,"(may Allah be well pleased with her):\n""The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) used to eat watermelon with ripe dates.”"
194,I saw Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace) combine watermelon and ripe dates.”
195,“The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) ate watermelon with ripe dates.”
196,"“When the people saw the first fruit  and Your Prophet, and I am Your servant and Your Prophet. He supplicated You on behalf of Mecca, and I supplicate You on behalf of Medina, for the like of what he supplicated You for on behalf of Mecca, and the like thereof as well!’ Then he would summon the youngest child he saw and give him that fruit.”"
197,"Mu'adh ibn 'Afra sent me with a tray of ripe dates, and on it there were pieces of fluffy cucumber. He  (Allah bless him and give him peace) used to love cucumbers, so I brought them to him. He had with him some ornaments that had come to him from Bahrain, so he took a handful of them and gave it to me."
198,"I brought the Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) a tray of ripe dates and fluffy cucumber, so he gave me a handful of ornaments, or she said: of gold.”"
